message.content:
To identify assets held for sale in the ordinary course of business, in production for such sale, or in the process of being manufactured, we primarily look at the line item related to inventory.

- Inventory represents assets held for sale or in production.
- Initial value of Inventory from the data: 0.00 (2023-12-31)
- End value of Inventory from the data: 9,100,000.00 (2024-02-05)

No other line items directly represent assets held for sale or in production/manufacturing (e.g., no separate "Assets held for sale" or similar noted).

Hence:

```json
{"solution": {"initial value": "0.00", "end value": "9100000.00"}}
```
